6b83362c-b407-45a0-b1e6-e073a7d6e062.text: I'm currently working on adding new pool and coins to the app. The next version should come with Hiveon support, but don't worry, many more are coming after that! Alephium miners and Nanopool users will soon get full support from Hashrate!
